<plot>When Monica was six years old she got ill by poliomyelitis, in 1957. Confined to a wheelchair and in spite of severe drawbacks she managed to develop her own life. When she became a mother in 1990, she also had the initiative to make a documentary film about other women in her condition, with the help of her husband filmmaker.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?351349</url></doc>
